fields.title: Cloudy sky in Thuringia Germany
fields.description: I wanted capture this serene landscape for a while now showing the tranquil woods, aa gentle river meanders through the landscape, its crystal-clear waters shimmering in the sunlight provided extra lighting reflecting the surrounding trees like a mirror. I used  my sigma wide length lens so as to portray the river's path as it twists and turns, carving its way through the heart of the forest, . The cloud above it provided a calm but mysterious mood in the picture.

fields.title: Essence of  Innocence
fields.description: I enjoy photographing human beings. When i see young children in my travels I like to capture their joyous and carefree nature. With just one shot I can evoke feelings of innocence, vitality, and positivity.
